data.description: Welcome to 212 Hatfield Dr, a charming residence nestled in the heart of Ringgold, GA. This inviting home offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, this ranch style home features a screened in back porch, 2 car garage, and a fenced in, private backyard! It is located in the Hatfield Acres subdivision. This home provides the ideal setting for comfortable living and entertaining!
